description: Stylish 2-bed, 2-bath unit with deeded garage parking and private balcony is now available! The unit features a custom chef’s kitchen with waterfall quartz counters, Thermador appliances, in-unit laundry, ample storage, a heated bathroom floor, and hardwood floors throughout. This 2018 build is in a prime South Boston location with easy access to the Red Line, South End, Seaport, and Downtown Boston. Come take a tour!
